title: He resigns the cowboys against Detroit Lyons' rule after they reach $500,000.
subtitle: :: Rumours: The National Football Association of the House of Morelli resigned after paying him $500,000 for his appointment to the 2014 final match for cowboys and leagues.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The Reign (Pete Morelli) resigned after paying him $500,000 to install him in the final match of 2014 between the cowboys and the herders.
